upcomming.title: Onam Celebration
upcomming.description: Join us for a grand celebration of Onam, Kerala's most vibrant and culturally rich festival! This year's Onam event promises to be a joyous occasion filled with traditional festivities, delicious cuisine, and a strong sense of community spirit.

upcomming.title: Christmas Celebration
upcomming.description: Celebrate the magic of Christmas with us at our annual Christmas event! This year, we are planning a festive extravaganza filled with joy, laughter, and holiday cheer. Bring your family and friends to enjoy a memorable day of Christmas activities and celebrations
